summary:
- **Class Action Against N.M. Super/AMP Superannuation**: Filed in Federal Court (Victoria) alleging higher life insurance premiums charged to certain members (2019–2024). AMP entities will defend.  
- **Dexus Legal Proceeding**: Filed in NSW Supreme Court against AMP entities re: Macquarie Shopping Centre sale dispute. AMP will defend.  

*No material financial impacts quantified; disclosures limited to legal defence stance.*
